  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "Install and use @phosphor-icons/react or lucide-react for icons.",
    "Use framer-motion for subtle entrance animations (fade up on scroll).",
    "Ensure the contact form uses Shadcn components and has a layout ready for MongoDB/Resend integration.",
    "Implement a language toggle (visual only, or state-based) in the header for English/Hindi.",
    "Include a 'Download Brochure' button in the navigation or hero section.",
    "Add 'data-testid' to all interactive elements (buttons, form inputs, toggles).",
    "Use pure Tailwind/HTML for the marketing layout, avoiding rigid Shadcn containers for full-width sections."
  ]
